# Brand name: LeoVer

Always write the product/brand name as **LeoVer** (capital **L** and capital **V**).

Never write: Leover, leover, LEOVER, LeoVerApp as "Leover", etc.

Applies to:
- User-facing copy (UI strings, emails, docs, commit messages when mentioning the brand)
- Comments and documentation in this repo when referring to the product name

Technical identifiers may keep existing package/module names if already established (e.g. `com.comunidapp.app`), but any human-readable brand mention must be **LeoVer**.
